These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, white, turquise, lavender
House: colonial, craftsman, wooden, modern
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, trance, reggae, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: german, pakistani, russian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, snowboarding, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 2. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 5. the modern house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 6. the wooden house is on the left of the modern house##1
 7. the wooden house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 9. the person who likes white is the wooden house##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
11. the german is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
12. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
13. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of trance##1
14. the turkish is on the far left##1
15. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |       3       |        4        |
| Color      | lavender    | turquise        | white | azure     |
| House          | colonial    | craftsman  | wooden     | modern          |
| Music-Genre           | trance | reggae     | funk    | hip-hop |
| Nationality   | turkish     | pakistani    | russian       | german          |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | snowboarding | sailing       | surfing         |

