.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, green, grey
There 4 different types of food: apple, carrot, cucumber, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, magic-tricks, photography, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, family, disaster
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, chaman, montecristo
 1. the montecristo-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 5. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
11. the person eating radish is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the vegafina-smoker##2
13. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |      2      |      3       |      4       |
| Color   | azure        | green    | grey        | mauve         |
| Food       | cucumber   | carrot      | radish       | apple        |
| Hobby      | card-games | photography | video-games  | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre        | disaster  | satire   | zombie   | family     |
| Cigar      | montecristo | vegafina    | chaman | havana       |

