 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 7. the russian is between the owner of the lizard and the thai##2
 8. the owner of the dog is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the owner of the dog is the owner of the dog##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
11. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
12. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the indian##3
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |     4     |
