 8. the person playing go is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person who likes white is the person playing chess##1
10. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
11. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
13. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
14. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
